'''AACS LA''' ('''Advanced Access Content System Licensing Administrator''') is the body that develops and licenses the [[Advanced Access Content System|AACS]] copy-protection system used on the [[HD DVD]] and [[Blu-ray Disc]] high-definition optical disc formats.

