'''Fentin acetate''' is an [[organotin compound]] with the formula (C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>)<sub>3</sub>SnO<sub>2</sub>CCH<sub>3</sub>. It is a colourless solid that was previously used as a [[fungicide]].<ref>G. G. Graf "Tin, Tin Alloys, and Tin Compounds" in ''Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry'', 2005, Wiley-VCH.{{doi|10.1002/14356007.a27_049}}</ref>

